different guises.

17
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:45,990
They are also the foundation
of the field of inference.

18
00:00:45,990 --> 00:00:49,970
And we will see how they
arise in that context.

19
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:53,780
Then, in the second lecture of
this unit, we will consider a

20
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,860
